SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight], [t].[Id], [t].[Code], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[IngredientId], [t1].[CompanyId], [t1].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t] ON [d].[CategoriesId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AvgPrice], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t0] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t1] ON [d].[Id] = [t1].[DishId]
WHERE [d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0
ORDER BY [d].[Id], [t].[Id], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[IngredientId], [t1].[Id]

SELECT [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight], [t].[Id], [t].[Code], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[IngredientId], [t1].[CompanyId], [t1].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t] ON [d].[CategoriesId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t0].[Id], [t0].[AvgPrice], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t0].[MeasureUnit], [t0].[Name], [t0].[StockDate], [t0].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t0] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t1] ON [d].[Id] = [t1].[DishId]
WHERE [d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0
ORDER BY [d].[Id], [t].[Id], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[IngredientId], [t1].[Id]

) AS [t]

    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]

        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]

    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight]

    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]

    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]

    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]

    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(2) [c].[Id], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[DishesQuantity], [c].[Name], [c].[Price]
    FROM [Complex] AS [c]
    WHERE (([c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([c].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([c].[Id] = @__id_1)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[DishId], [d].[ComplexId], [d].[DishCourse], [d].[CompanyId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DishComplex] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CategoriesId], [d0].[Code], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Description], [d0].[KKal], [d0].[Name], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[Price], [d0].[ReadyWeight]

        WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[DishId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ComplexId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoriesId], [t].[Code], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Description], [t].[KKal], [t].[Name], [t].[PictureId], [t].[Price], [t].[ReadyWeight], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Name], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[CompanyId], [t2].[Proportion], [t2].[Id], [t2].[AvgPrice], [t2].[CompanyId0], [t2].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t2].[MeasureUnit], [t2].[Name], [t2].[StockDate], [t2].[StockValue]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[DishesQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[ComplexId], [t1].[DishCourse], [t1].[CompanyId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Code], [t1].[CompanyId0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[KKal], [t1].[Name], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ReadyWeight]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[DishId], [d].[ComplexId], [d].[DishCourse], [d].[CompanyId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DishComplex] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CategoriesId], [d0].[Code], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Description], [d0].[KKal], [d0].[Name], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[Price], [d0].[ReadyWeight]

    WHERE [d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ComplexId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoriesId], [t].[Code], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Description], [t].[KKal], [t].[Name], [t].[PictureId], [t].[Price], [t].[ReadyWeight], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Name], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[CompanyId], [t2].[Proportion], [t2].[Id], [t2].[AvgPrice], [t2].[CompanyId0], [t2].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t2].[MeasureUnit], [t2].[Name], [t2].[StockDate], [t2].[StockValue]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]

        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]

    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]

    WHERE (([c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([c].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([c].[Id] = @__id_1)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[DishId], [d].[ComplexId], [d].[DishCourse], [d].[CompanyId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DishComplex] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CategoriesId], [d0].[Code], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Description], [d0].[KKal], [d0].[Name], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[Price], [d0].[ReadyWeight]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ComplexId]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

(DbType = Int32), @__id_1='?' (DbType = Int32), @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[DishesQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[ComplexId], [t1].[DishCourse], [t1].[CompanyId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Code], [t1].[CompanyId0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[KKal], [t1].[Name], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [c].[Id], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[DishesQuantity], [c].[Name], [c].[Price]
    FROM [Complex] AS [c]
    WHERE (([c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([c].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([c].[Id] = @__id_1)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[DishId], [d].[ComplexId], [d].[DishCourse], [d].[CompanyId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ReadyWeight]

    INNER JOIN (

) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]

(DbType = Int32)], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoriesId], [t].[Code], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[Description], [t].[KKal], [t].[Name], [t].[PictureId], [t].[Price], [t].[ReadyWeight], [t0].[Id], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId], [t0].[Description], [t0].[Name], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[CompanyId], [t2].[Proportion], [t2].[Id], [t2].[AvgPrice], [t2].[CompanyId0], [t2].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t2].[MeasureUnit], [t2].[Name], [t2].[StockDate], [t2].[StockValue]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [Dishes] AS [d]
    WHERE ([d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([d].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)
) AS [t]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2

2020-07-10 16:21:19.722 +03:00 [Information] Microsoft.EntityFrameworkCore.Database.Command: Executed DbCommand (32ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']

IF EXISTS
    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]
         WHERE [ep].[major_id] = [o].[object_id]
             AND [ep].[minor_id] = 0
             AND [ep].[class] = 1
             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'
    )

) AS [t]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CompanyId], [t].[DishesQuantity], [t].[Name], [t].[Price], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[ComplexId], [t1].[DishCourse], [t1].[CompanyId], [t1].[Id], [t1].[CategoriesId], [t1].[Code], [t1].[CompanyId0], [t1].[Description], [t1].[KKal], [t1].[Name], [t1].[PictureId], [t1].[Price], [t1].[ReadyWeight]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [c].[Id], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[DishesQuantity], [c].[Name], [c].[Price]
    FROM [Complex] AS [c]
    WHERE (([c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_0) AND ([c].[CompanyId] = @__companyId_0)) AND ([c].[Id] = @__id_1)
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[DishId], [d].[ComplexId], [d].[DishCourse], [d].[CompanyId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ReadyWeight]
    FROM [DishComplex] AS [d]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CategoriesId], [d0].[Code], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Description], [d0].[KKal], [d0].[Name], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[Price], [d0].[ReadyWeight]
        FROM [Dishes] AS [d0]
        WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
    ) AS [t0] ON [d].[DishId] = [t0].[Id]
    WHERE [d].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ComplexId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t1].[DishId], [t1].[ComplexId], [t1].[DishCourse], [t1].[Id]

    FROM [Categories] AS [c]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]

        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[DishId], [d].[ComplexId], [d].[DishCourse], [d].[CompanyId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ReadyWeight]

        SELECT [d0].[Id], [d0].[CategoriesId], [d0].[Code], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Description], [d0].[KKal], [d0].[Name], [d0].[PictureId], [d0].[Price], [d0].[ReadyWeight]

) AS [t1] ON [t].[Id] = [t1].[ComplexId]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (

) AS [t]

    SELECT [c].[Id], [c].[Code], [c].[CompanyId], [c].[Description], [c].[Name]
    FROM [Categories] AS [c]
    WHERE [c].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_1
) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

    SELECT [d].[DishId], [d].[ComplexId], [d].[DishCourse], [d].[CompanyId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ReadyWeight]

    SELECT TOP(@__p_1) [d].[Id], [d].[CategoriesId], [d].[Code], [d].[CompanyId], [d].[Description], [d].[KKal], [d].[Name], [d].[PictureId], [d].[Price], [d].[ReadyWeight]

) AS [t]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (

) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

    (SELECT *
     FROM [sys].[objects] o
     WHERE [o].[type] = 'U'
     AND [o].[is_ms_shipped] = 0
     AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT *
         FROM [sys].[extended_properties] AS [ep]

             AND [ep].[name] = N'microsoft_database_tools_support'

) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d0].[DishId], [d0].[IngredientId], [d0].[CompanyId], [d0].[Proportion], [t1].[Id], [t1].[AvgPrice], [t1].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t1].[IngredientCategoriesId], [t1].[MeasureUnit], [t1].[Name], [t1].[StockDate], [t1].[StockValue]
    FROM [DishIngredients] AS [d0]
    INNER JOIN (
        SELECT [i].[Id], [i].[AvgPrice], [i].[CompanyId], [i].[IngredientCategoriesId], [i].[MeasureUnit], [i].[Name], [i].[StockDate], [i].[StockValue]
        FROM [Ingredients] AS [i]
        WHERE [i].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_3
    ) AS [t1] ON [d0].[IngredientId] = [t1].[Id]
    WHERE [d0].[CompanyId] = @__ef_filter__CompanyId_2
) AS [t2] ON [t].[Id] = [t2].[DishId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t0].[Id], [t2].[DishId], [t2].[IngredientId], [t2].[Id]

) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [d].[DishId], [d].[ComplexId], [d].[DishCourse], [d].[CompanyId], [t0].[Id], [t0].[CategoriesId], [t0].[Code], [t0].[CompanyId] AS [CompanyId0], [t0].[Description], [t0].[KKal], [t0].[Name], [t0].[PictureId], [t0].[Price], [t0].[ReadyWeight]

) AS [t0] ON [t].[CategoriesId] = [t0].[Id]
